    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out under MRL 2 guidance for a Class II device with medium model influence. The CFD model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions under the stated COU. The relative hemolysis index criterion RH < 1 is supported by validated NIH predictions within 28% of experimental data across all 5 operating points.",
